high_descs: Turn to the right, and then the right again to locate the white table.
Pick up the spoon and cup from the middle of the table.
Carry the spoon and cup and turn around, then left to find the stove.
Place the spoon and cup on the counter to the left of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Move a spoon and cup from a table to the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward to the dining table, then turn right and walk to the other dining table against the wall.
Pick up the black cup with a spoon in it from the table.
Turn right and walk forward to the counter to the left of the stove top.
Put the cup on the counter, just to the right of the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a spoon in it on a counter top.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the white table.
Turn around and stand between the stove and the fridge.
Put the pot on the counter between the stove and the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot on the counter between the stove and the fridge.
